cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.NE, cs.CY 

This paper discusses the mechanisms of curiosity-driven learning using concepts and tools from machine learning and developmental robotics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CY (Computational Complexity).
